What is DevOps?

DevOps stands for Development and Operations

It is a methodology in the Software development and IT industry. It is used as a set of practices and tools; DevOps integrates and automates the work of software development
and IT operations as a means for improving and shortening the system development life cycle

In Simple words, it is colloboration of development and operations team for the improvement of design, development, and delivery of the application.

DEVOPS WITH THE PURPOSE OF DESIGNING, DEVELOPMENT, AND APPLICATION OR SOFTWARE DELIVERY
